Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的村子已经在400年间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断和外界的接触  过着自给自足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓夏至祭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是迎接在夏天回来的先祖们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷丰收的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从明天的黎明开始  夜晚结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们可以待到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊  那玫瑰窗和尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以前绘画里的中世纪教堂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这边的也很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个水井真是老古董啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带的山里住着野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这村里住着的人不就是狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么  我们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使和下面的人种族不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和柯蒂丽亚长得一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那时我还是个孩子  但我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她给这间宅子  这个村子带来了无法消除的灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荷曼妮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.69,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(653,545)}在夏至祭降下神谕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件发生在狄奥多村长的书房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜里十二点在书房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女仆…对了  当时还是十五岁的柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有去更换水壶里的水的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天也正好是在十二点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和其他人看到了打开锁进去的柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我用怀表确认了一下时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知为何  和我一起的人对时间的证词都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入书房的柯蒂丽亚马上就发出了尖叫  跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匆忙赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄奥多村长已经被短刀刺中身亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地板上不知为何散落着很多金币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金币？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为这个村子不使用金币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时都由狄奥多村长统一保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天晚上开始  柯蒂丽亚就发高烧卧床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到她退烧  成为下一任村长的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将她放逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐出？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她拿着一枚金币和一只旅行箱离开村子之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就升起了那座吊桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未离开过村子不谙世事的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都怀疑她能不能平安活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则会给村里带来灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那个柯蒂丽亚的女儿却在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散什么步啊  明明刚刚才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谢尔吉斯村长的助手  安普罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  为什么皮肤和头发的颜色不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我知道外面世界的人不都只是金发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加  帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个地方想让你给我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  可以让我再摸这个人一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯蒂丽亚住过的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟带我们来这种地方被人知道了可不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是柯蒂丽亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和还是婴儿的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是柯蒂丽亚十五岁时就被赶出这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带走了留在这里的什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后留下了长大后柯蒂丽亚的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混沌究竟指向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄奥多…前任村长的墓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对坟墓做这种遭天谴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我不是罪人  C」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯蒂丽亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是柯蒂丽亚写下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲果然是因为冤罪被赶出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  真正的罪人会在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…和维多利加一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  电话怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜德蕊小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话也就是说  果然这里通着电吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  村长不是说过的是自给自足的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问了那个奇怪的女仆才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是有赞助人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞助人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  名字叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个叫布莱恩·罗斯可的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱恩…罗斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是离开村子在外面生活的人的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约在十年前他出了一笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牌也打腻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  去教堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚刚有狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西  那个可怕的老头会把它们赶跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又缠到一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系带和荷叶边太多叫人头晕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前来的布莱恩·罗斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是为了什么目的来到这个村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了给村里拉电线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到十年前  就是上次世界大战发生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得这个时代给深山里拉电线太匆忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  十年前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也符合那张照片拍摄的年代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是洗澡的热水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请掺入凉水使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有澡可以洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加  发生什么事的话要叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里守着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  哦  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}我喜欢洗澡～啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}因为暖洋洋～啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  是唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于像是变回平时的维多利加了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了久城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想吓唬我  把我从村里赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧  这个村子有种不祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会保护我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  这是红芜菁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台花车是冬之军的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬之军？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  在这个广场上村里的男人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会分为夏之军和冬之军演一场打仗的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏之军要把冬之军的主将冬之男打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和花车一起点火烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要侮辱这个村子的话就滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无聊  相信迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个晦气的村子  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  要是现在被赶出这村子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙  到哪都是一副坏脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回房间去吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙昨晚也在教堂干了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在村里人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把装饰的古壶往装圣水的水缸里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗通一下丢了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发酒疯的话我可听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还笑着说「是这种破烂货  为什么还当宝」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣彼得也会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  祭典的点心  我拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说了那些话  果然还是在意祭典的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是安普罗兹先生吧  好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬之男啊  燃烧消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是假人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚  亚朗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算妨碍祭典来找茬而和假人交换了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔吉斯村长  那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在少女们扔榛果的时候  这个年轻人走过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广场也聚集了很多人  是不可能和假人交换的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴是愚者的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏至祭是不能中止的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来教堂还有仪式  我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都有人死了  居然还要继续祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很奇怪啊  这个村子里的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会保护我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一弥先生  你也是询问未来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏之军胜利了  约定丰收之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚时分就要将教堂清空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教堂是通往阴间的出入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成为来看丰收的祖先们的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  接近这里的祖先们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会通过村长回答孩子们的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一弥先生  机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是和维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等下  安普罗兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我是来找维多利加的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个女孩和你是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  我有一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道和维多利加以后也能一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在几年之后  会吹起撼动世界的狂风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的身体太轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那阵狂风  你们两人将会分开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  心将永远不会分离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问了能不能长高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长高是指什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身高！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是受尽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不说一声说就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才都跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄奥多村长就这样被刺中后背  那把短刀直没到刀柄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄奥多大人是成年人  柯蒂丽亚是十五岁的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身高差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  对孩子够不到的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能将短刀插没到刀柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人柯蒂丽亚  那污秽的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果  或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人另有其人  你是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智慧之泉在对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在碎片全部重新拼凑完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新拼凑完成  那知道谁是犯人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算知道谁是犯人  证明它的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有人死了  就算狼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏至祭也不允许中止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经听不到狼的声音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了  安普罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第二个了  久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的罪恶闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的罪恶将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会  有非常不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:21.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(641,556)}过去的王国里回荡着长啸
